column6:
Dear Thrilisell,

I have recently purchased 30 pieces of the touch-sensitive modular lighting (Order #2062, shipping to São Paulo, Brazil), and noticed, afterwards, that it comes with only one power cable, so that the set of 30 pieces should always be kept together.

My original intention was to divide the 30 pieces and put each group of pieces in different spots in my bedroom.

Therefore I was wondering if you could just cancel the purchase and reverse the payment to my credit card, so that I buy 2 sets of 16 pieces instead (or perhaps even 3 sets of 10 pieces), or maybe you could just find a way to send me extra power cables, I don't know.

Also, the lights seem yellow in some pictures, and white in others, which may deceive some customers, so do keep that in mind in the future.


Thanks in advance and I hope we can solve this properly,

Lucas

Dear Suppliers,

Good evening.

This morning I made a purchase of two units of a product sold by you (composter), which I saw in an ad for a third-party application that I had just downloaded from the Google Store.

It was an impulse purchase.

During the course of the period I reflected better and conclude that I should not have done this for several reasons:

I already use a homemade compost system that has satisfactorily supplied my needs;
The environmental cost (ecological footprint) for the production, transportation and delivery of the product in my home does not compensate the impact to be avoided with its use;
I do not have any money available to pay the credit card bill.

Therefore, I ask you kindly to cancel the purchase transaction that I have made immediately. I also ask you to inform the operator of my credit card about the withdrawal, in order to avoid launching the charge on the next invoice.


I take this message to let you know that I did not receive any kind of electronic message in my mailbox about this operation. As I had made the purchase through third-party app advertisement (sudoku.com), if I had not made a screen image at the time of the transaction, I would not have found the channel of your contact, as my card operator credit reported that the transaction is in the name of "SC Online Paym", whose search in the world computer network was negative.

If you have any questions or would like to contact me, you can do so by calling 55 67 9 9984 3880 or by e-mail sergio@capille.com.br, as registered in my ShopMyBest account.

Lastly, I would be grateful if you would confirm receipt of this message.

Sorry for the inconvenience and thank you for understanding.

Sergio

column4: I wish to order cancellation ID: # 21882
column6:
Dear Suppliers ShopMyBest.Com,

Good evening.

1. Complementing and reiterating my previous message, sent by the channel
"contac us" of the site <
https://www.shopmybest.com/index.php?route=information/contact>, INFORM
that::

1.1. This morning I made the *purchase (ID: # 21882*, US $ 139.80) of two
units of a product offered by you (composter), which I had seen in an
advertisement for one third-party app (sudoku.com) that I just purchased
from the Google Store.


1.2. I made the purchase on impulse and, after reflecting on my action, I
am sorry and decided to cancel my order, for several reasons:


1.2.1. The environmental cost (ecological footprint) for producing,
transporting, delivering and using the product you offer will outweigh the
impact avoided by its use;

1.2.2. I already own and use a domestic composting system that is more
rudimentary but satisfies my needs;

1.2.3. I do not have the money available to pay the credit card bill.


2. Thus, I APPLY:

2.1. *Cancel immediately the purchase transaction performed by me* and
mentioned in item 1.1, above.

2.2. Inform the operator of this transaction about the withdrawal of this
acquisition, making it clear that the charge on my credit card should not
be made.


3. I take this message to let you know that* I did not receive any kind of
electronic message in my mailbox about this operation*. As I had made the
purchase through third-party app advertisement (sudoku.com), if I had not
made a screen image at the time of the transaction, I would not have found
the channel of your contact, as my card operator credit reported that the
transaction is in the name of "SC Online Paym", whose search in the world
computer network was negative.

*3.1. If you have any questions or would like to contact me, you can do so
by calling 55 67 9 9984 3880 or by e-mail sergio@capille.com.br
<sergio@capille.com.br>, as registered in my ShopMyBest account.*


4. Lastly, I would be grateful if you would confirm receipt of this message.
